<h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

Pente.org will not send you unsolicited emails, or give your email address to anyone
without your permission.  Pente.org, or other players here, may send you emails at
the address provided in the following cases:<br>
<ul>
 <li>You will receive a welcome email from Pente.org with your player name and password</li>
 <li>If you forget your password and request it, it will be sent to you via email</li>
 <li>If you are playing a game and click <b>Email Game</b>, a text representation
     of the game will be sent to you via email</li>
 <li>If you choose to have Pente.org News mailed to you,
     you will receive news about rarely via email</li>
 <li>If another player knows your player name, they can send you a message
     that will show up under "My Messages".  If you want to have these messages
     also sent to you via email you can configure that</li>
 <li>If you "watch" a topic at the Forums and configure your profile to send
     emails when the topic is updated, you will get an email with the update</li>
 <li>If you play in a tournament, the tournament directors will correspond with
     you about matches via email</li>
 <li>If you choose to display your email address on your profile <b>any</b> registered
     player will be able to view it!</li>
</ul>

